{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "64b169d1f23ac7d519f9aebd", "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 3, "category": null, "approximateTimeRequired": 180, "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "source": "MOG", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76cfc52ffa3c944600e0"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fec2b295b085ab6eb8e"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "microConcepts": [], "questionLabels": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "620a8a1e77301f65c2f92c40", "title": "JEE Advanced 2007 (Paper 1)", "isVisible": true}], "question": {"text": "Two particles of mass $m$ each are tied at the ends of a light string of length $2 a$. The whole system is kept on a frictionless horizontal surface with the string held tight so that each mass is at a distance $a$ from the centre $P$ (as shown in the figure). Now, the mid-point of the string is pulled vertically upwards with a small but constant force $F$. As a result, the particles move towards each other on the surface.\nThe magnitude of acceleration, when the separation between them becomes $2 x$, is\n<img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/jee_advanced/Q_K7C81tVdzEH0oCE0tZ6FId-Hb5SBLzFb6esDvD5mM.original.fullsize.png\"><br>", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "yQOVu", "text": "\n$\\frac{F}{2 m} \\frac{a}{\\sqrt{a^2-x^2}}$\n", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "SuRdQ", "text": "\n$\\frac{F}{2 m} \\frac{x}{\\sqrt{a^2-x^2}}$\n", "image": null, "isCorrect": true}, {"id": "JDHRS", "text": "\n$\\frac{F}{2 m} \\frac{x}{a}$\n", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "SAWJF", "text": "\n$\\frac{F}{2 m} \\frac{\\sqrt{a^2-x^2}}{x}$", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "6.\n$$\n\\begin{aligned}\n& 2 T \\cos \\theta=F \\\\\n& \\therefore T=\\frac{F}{2} \\sec \\theta \\\\\n& \\text { Acceleration of particle }=\\frac{T \\sin \\theta}{m}=\\frac{F \\tan \\theta}{2 m}=\\frac{F}{2 m} \\frac{x}{\\sqrt{a^2-x^2}}\n\\end{aligned}\n$$\n\n$$\n\\therefore \\text { Option (b) is correct. }\n$$\n<img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/jee_advanced/czDNFTSOTpo3yxad4winPks0pMRQkvnS2fZ-aupjRsk.original.fullsize.png\"><br>", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "masterId": "MOGJAPYQ27002786", "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "bucket": "", "isRemoved": false, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87e3e15", "616057190283de43c87e3e18", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd7", "64d50bd73df7f4a7f3017f6f", "66b79b34d4b564dfab4f94cc", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc11", "67fa5fef4468eb1307ceb0ad", "6807d2ad647479b8e8696479"], "cpyqbChapters": ["616023b74026d68c120f2ba9", "616023b9c2e3bbfc3f2ecdd2", "616023b78dba43da23bef37e", "616023b542cfec4323be20b3", "61964c74ec1ca6c1a7365dcf", "61bb821fa52006d37a60e707", "61c089a30f62a0d239520145", "61964c76bae973f89e899882", "61e7bd7991a3d691658409aa", "616023b36f5a53c6a5d4ce42", "629f3a90cf4faea06a760897", "629109ec048d30f09d45ec7c", "629621223df2fbbc95bf297f", "629f390ce1a391b9376aa0de", "64eb06e13118f713ecfef1d7", "66d58567a75f05ee8564f723", "67921d641d5b5072da5e9aaa", "67fdff50378e1624ea7b6a0d", "680920323a10446a207fdf3e"], "cpyqbExams": ["616059150283de43c87e3e21"]}, "fetch_status": true}